rt of the epic isn't getting the people together...it's findin the mob up.  the trigger for the golem that drops the green oil is on a 3 day timer and usually killed w/in a couple hours of spawing.  anytime you're on you should do whatever you can to check to see if he's up, and just get a group together when you find him.  it's almost impossible to plan a hit time for him.  fortunately, this hit can be done w/ as few as a single group of pactum people if you got the right classes, and almost any decent combination of 2 groups.<br>
<br>
strat for tracking him:<br>
<br>
ask a ranger to come w/ you to fear, get all the  hp/ac/rune buffs you can find, head down to fear, both of you zone in invis.  ranger tracks.  RANGER DROPS INVIS FIRST.  this is important so that ranger takes initial aggro, then you cast evac to another zone.  so far, this has worked for me and although i've never found him up we've not had any tracking casualties yet.<br>
<br>
the biggest danger here is the scarelings that see invis and proc yonder on you.  alayna almost missed port last time cause she got ported away from me.  just make sure you are both aware that you can be ported and find your way back to the hill as soon as possible.<br>
<br>
xeno spent a year trying to get up w/ this mob....hoping it takes the rest of us less time.<br>
<br>
good luck. <p>Nae</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub8.ezboard.com/bpactum1557.showUserPublicProfile?gid=corpsedagain>CorpsedAgain</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 1288<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(5/20/03 2:39 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub8.ezboard.com/fpactum1557frm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=174.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: doing the epic thing</span><hr size=1> Mnsain spent like...2 years.  Least it seemed like it. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=198911">Corpsed</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub8.ezboard.com/bpactum1557.showUserPublicProfile?gid=chracner>Chracner</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 65<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(5/20/03 10:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub8.ezboard.com/fpactum1557frm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=174.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: doing the epic thing</span><hr size=1> When ya find the mob up Scots, I will be there to lay the Chrac down on him with ya. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=203631">Chracner</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
